\name{rdcor-package}
\alias{rdcor-package}
\docType{package}
\title{
Rank Distance Correlation Coefficient
}
\description{
The rank distance correlation of Shi H., Drton M. and Han F. (2022) is computed. Included also is a function to perform permutation based testing.
